    <item>
      <title>他信 37 岁女儿即将出任泰国新总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/thaksin-s-37-year-old-daughter-set-to-become-new-thai-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦的女儿即将成为这个东南亚国家的下一任总理，这意味着在周三另一名党内成员被赶下台后，政策将保持连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/thaksin-s-37-year-old-daughter-set-to-become-new-thai-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯以叛国罪判处美国双重国籍者 12 年徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/russia-sentences-us-dual-citizen-to-12-years-in-treason-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯法院以叛国罪判处拥有俄罗斯和美国双重国籍的克谢尼娅·卡列琳娜 12 年监禁，罪名是她向帮助乌克兰的慈善机构捐款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/russia-sentences-us-dual-citizen-to-12-years-in-treason-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 09:44:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国药品价格措施将在 2026 年降低 75 亿美元成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/us-drug-price-negotiations-cut-costs-7-5-billion-in-first-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府表示，美国政府具有里程碑意义的药品价格谈判将在其生效的第一年为美国人节省75亿美元，这是降低其全球最高药品费用的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/us-drug-price-negotiations-cut-costs-7-5-billion-in-first-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
